eres, we show that chemical relaxation is mostly accurate to within an\norder of magnitude, a factor of 2 and $\\sim 10\\%$, respectively. The level of\naccuracy attained allows for the chemical relaxation method to be included in\nthree-dimensional general circulation models.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 22 Nov 2017 20:11:53 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 29 May 2018 17:30:25 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-08-01"}
