bution and show that the CDW state in TiSe$_2$ is of a bond-type and\ninduces a vortex-like antiferroelectric polarization in the kagome network of\nTi atoms.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 23 Nov 2017 01:14:27 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 17 Apr 2018 09:13:09 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-04-18"}
